POMP
====

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following in this ditribution's root directory:

	$ cpan . # install deps, make, make test, make install

You can also do this manually:
	
	$ perl Makefile.PL
	$ make
	$ make test
	$ make install # optional but you will have to use -Mblib


DEPENDENCIES

This program requires these other modules and libraries:

	Parse::Yapp
	Text::Balanced
	Template::Toolkit


